title: The Cub & The Caterpillar: Episode Seven Pt. Two
itunes:title: The Cub & The Caterpillar: Episode Seven Pt. Two
description:
Our heroes face off with a giant ape, meet new friends, and head towards the Twin Pea- er, White Twins in this exciting conclusion to last week’s episode of The Cub and the Caterpillar: A Wagadu Tale!


If you enjoy this podcast please help us out by leaving a review and sharing with your fellow adventurers.

Support us on Patreon at patreon.com/tbhalflings for access to our post-show discussion, The Wagadu Watch, Bonus Episodes and your Shirefolk Shoutout.
